race.comment: BEEN A SECRET (5) resumes back in grade and performs fresh. She placed at her only go at 1000m and gets in well with the 3kg claim. Will go close if she's wound up. TURN UP THE MUSIC (7) turned in a nice effort to score here two runs ago but was less effective last time, placing second behind a dominant winner. Keeps the handy 2kg claim and races forward. Worth another chance. STILLWELL (6) has trialled well for his return and gets in well with the 3kg claim. He's proven fresh and should be around the mark. GIGGY (10) keeps the 2kg claim, and his close-up placing here two back would have him in contention.
